sentences: Adnan Hamidović (born 31 May 1982), better known by his stage name Frenkie, is a Bosnian rapper from Tuzla.
As of 2019, he has recorded six successful full-length albums to date: Odličan CD (2005),  Povratak Cigana (2007), Protuotrov (2009), Troyanac (2012),Egzil (2017) and Stari Frenkie (2021).
